first check the name of your adapter. in this case we want ethernet


Get-NetAdapter | format-table


let's say our adapter has as name 'Ethernet'

to disable it:

Disable-NetAdatper -Name "Ethernet" -Confirm:$false

to enable it:

Enable-NetAdatper -Name "Ethernet" -Confirm:$false

now you can create your shortcuts to run it quickly 
